## G.45 Deep-seed — a mnemonic

For remembering the general reflex in order:

**B I C T F** — Bind, Introspect, Compare, Trace, Fix.

Bind the value. Introspect it. Compare to expectations. Trace back to the source. Fix.

Five letters. Say them the first time you hit a bug. By the tenth time you will be doing the five steps without saying anything.

## G.46 A closing exercise

For your next Motoi debug session, consciously follow BICTF. Notice where you skip steps or reorder them. Notice which recipes apply. That awareness accelerates the reflex.

